trans-unit.source: Provides information about a field of a type that components can access across application domain and process boundaries.
trans-unit.target: 提供元件可以存取跨應用程式定義域和處理序界限的類型欄位的相關資訊。

trans-unit.source: The RemoteFieldData structure provides information about a field of a remote type that implements the <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Automation.IRemoteTypeContract> interface.
trans-unit.target: RemoteFieldData 結構提供欄位的相關資訊之型別的遠端實作<xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Automation.IRemoteTypeContract>介面。</xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Automation.IRemoteTypeContract>

trans-unit.source: Represents the attributes of the field that this <xref href="System.AddIn.Contract.Automation.RemoteFieldData"></xref> describes.
trans-unit.target: 代表欄位的屬性這<xref href="System.AddIn.Contract.Automation.RemoteFieldData"></xref>描述。

trans-unit.source: This field is not used if this <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Automation.RemoteFieldData> describes a field of a COM object.
trans-unit.target: 此欄位不是此<xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Automation.RemoteFieldData>描述 COM 物件的欄位。</xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Automation.RemoteFieldData>

trans-unit.source: Represents the type of the value of the field that this <xref href="System.AddIn.Contract.Automation.RemoteFieldData"></xref> describes.
trans-unit.target: 代表類型的欄位值的這個<xref href="System.AddIn.Contract.Automation.RemoteFieldData"></xref>描述。

trans-unit.source: Represents member data for the field that this <xref href="System.AddIn.Contract.Automation.RemoteFieldData"></xref> describes.
trans-unit.target: 代表成員欄位的資料，此<xref href="System.AddIn.Contract.Automation.RemoteFieldData"></xref>描述。

trans-unit.source: The member data includes the name of the field and the type that declares the field.
trans-unit.target: 這個成員資料包含欄位和欄位的宣告類型的名稱。
